text: Naomi Anne Folkard is an archer from Great Britain. She was born on 18 September 1983. Folkard competed at the 2004, 2008, 2012, 2016, and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Naomi Folkard == References == Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
